Works with FOCAL-65 for 6502 processors

10.1 T !"ENTER ORDER FOR OUTPUT OF CARPET."!; A R
10.2 T !; S S=3^R

11.1 F I=0,1,S-1; D 12; T !
11.2 Q

12.1 F J=0,1,S-1; D 13
12.2 R

13.1 S X=J, Y=I
13.2 D 15
13.3 I (C-1),13.6
13.4 T " "; R
13.6 T "#"; R

15.05 S C=0
15.1 S X3=FINT(X/3), Y3=FINT(Y/3)
15.2 S Z=(X-X3*3)*(Y-Y3*3)
15.3 I (Z-1) 15.4,15.9,15.4
15.4 S X=X3, Y=Y3
15.5 I (X) 15.6,15.6,15.1
15.6 I (Y) 15.7,15.7,15.1
15.7 S C=1
15.9 R
